Sundoggy/Sunkitty Privacy
We ask to use your current location to deliver an accurate forecast for that location.
We do not collect your location information, nor do we use it until the app is in the foreground.
We will not sell or give your location information or any logs of your usage of Sundoggy/Sunkitty to a third
      party.
      However, we may log certain events such as crashes for the purposes of improving the app.
Questions about this policy or the app can be addressed to
sundoggy@kenlaws.com